metadata.name: 1000 Dreams
metadata.description:
The official MEGAMI gallery now has 1,000 derivative creations, and many creators from the MEGAMI community collaborated to create this commemorative artwork for celebrating it. 

Creators and their creations are the driving force behind MEGAMI, and they are propelling this project forward. 
This is a historic milestone for MEGAMI and MEGAMIX, but our dreams still continue!

Here are the creators who participated in the collaborative artwork! 
@eminnisa_, @bandagenft, @iridori_nabe, @kura_matsuko, @zaiakuxx, @ppraewithme, @AyameHoon, @CATIST_NFT, @sage00444, @STEPiyoN, @WhoGoesSlowly, @evadachi59, @kurage_life_, @karindrops_nft, @sisosoup, @hiwana43, @chikuwanoe, @momofhiki, @somakuma2, @ren_hym_, @arito_hikaru, @koni_nft, @futaba_nft, @m1nm1ng3, @takefighterdqx, @MAcciNFT, @rienneit, @fujikart, @TAKE_NFT, @km_mmt, @2_kalistner, @_NaokiSaito, @arigieP, @AoyaNFT, @stellarcapitall, @aonisai_natuki
